WITH s AS (SELECT * FROM takes WHERE grade IS NOT NULL) SELECT * FROM s AS except

SELECT * FROM takes WHERE grade <> '' UNION SELECT * FROM takes WHERE (SELECT id FROM takes WHERE grade = '') NOT IN (SELECT id FROM takes WHERE grade <> '') AND (SELECT course_id FROM takes WHERE grade = '') NOT IN (SELECT course_id FROM takes WHERE grade <> '')
WITH passed AS (SELECT * FROM takes WHERE grade <> '') SELECT * FROM passed UNION SELECT * FROM takes WHERE grade = '' AND course_id NOT IN (SELECT course_id FROM passed)
